eo_data.Rd

imports data files from Eosense chambers

Usage

eo_data(path)

Arguments

path

location of the data files

Value

a dataframe with conitnuous measurement with timestamps

Examples

path <- system.file("extdata/ex_data", package = "readosense")
eo_data(path)
